=== Installation of Django + Django packages with pip ===

== Dependencies ==

sudo apt-get install python-pip
sudo pip install Django==1.7
sudo pip install django-polymorphic django-debug-toolbar django-erroneous \
django-registration-redux django-crispy-forms django-debug-toolbar \
django-floppyforms django-sendmail-backend \
mysql-connector-python pytz setuptools six South sqlparse

#New, Less->CSS-Compiler
sudo apt-get install node-less
sudo pip install django-static-precompiler


== Setup (Debug mode, Release mode require more steps) ==
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py createsuperuser


== Start ==
python manage.py runserver



